data.description: Price Reduced, Just under 2.5 acres! Gorgeous 3 bed, 3 bath home on 2.46 acres, is only 35 miles from Downtown Dallas. Beautifully renovated home was taken down to the studs and professionally remodeled with high end finishes in 2016. Open floor plan with fireplace, beautiful kitchen with ample cabinets, granite counter tops, new stove, dishwasher and microwave. Huge primary suite has dual sinks, granite countertops, large walk in shower, linen closet and large walk in custom closet. Additional spacious bedroom with ensuite full bath would be great for teens or in laws. Third large bedroom with walk in closet has easy access to full hall bath. Updates in 2016 include new roof, HVAC, aerobic septic, windows, cabinets, appliances, doors, bathrooms, flooring, sheetrock, Craftsman trim work, and the list goes on. Spacious 20x26 shop on slab with electricity, and 14x20 brick detached garage on slab with electricity and insulation, Wrought iron front fence with motorized gate. Move-in ready.
